Football is a team sport, and so is social change.

That’s why we’re teaming up with @CommonGoalOrg, pledging 1% of global net sales from Footballs to Common Goal from now until 2023, to help grow the movement that’s aiming to mobilize the whole football world to tackle our global challenges.

From fighting racism and discrimination, empowering gender equality, fostering mental well-being and promoting LGBTQ+ inclusion, we’re aiming to use the power of Football to positively impact 90,000 lives and move our communities forward.
 
#adidasFootballCollective
